"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-paris-2024-a-team-gb-medal-chance-per-day-at-olympic-games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Matt Hardy  Deputy Sports Editor - City AM  There is a lot going on at the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are 10,000 athletes looking to win one of just over 300 gold medals.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So here atCity A.M.we have picked a medal chance per day to keep your eyes on.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember London 2012 when Britain got their first medals in the men's time trials?\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.223757031909814e-14, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9999989952203169, \"rank\": 1.004780768052478e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well it is possible that this could repeat itself in Paris.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.584792822080896e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both the men's and women's trials get underway on Saturday afternoon.\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adam Peaty has faced some personal issues since Tokyo 2020 but he was the outstanding British qualifier for this event and one of the favourites for Sunday.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City\\u202fAM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's not beaten often and will undoubtedly plan on keeping his impressive Olympics record alive.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can Tom Daley win gold?\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1031, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3275134404303985e-51, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He goes early in the Olympic Games in the 10m synchronised diving competition.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At least if he loses he can knit himself a replacement medal\\u2026  Winner in the trial event in Paris last year, Alex Yee will go for gold in the men's triathlon.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1223, \"end\": 1228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.584792822080896e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1240, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the first Games since 2004 without one of the two Brownlee Brothers in the mix.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\", \"score\": 0.9995299304033408, \"rank\": 0.000469994677585034, \"text\": \"Brownlee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\"}, {\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"score\": 0.9999999984902388, \"rank\": 1.0896926568095861e-09, \"text\": \"Brothers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Straight after a Yee gold Team GB could pick up another first place in the female event.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1404, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999962178663, \"rank\": 3.340421591465083e-09, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The entire triathlon team is strong and Beth Potter will lead the Brits in the women's event.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beth Potter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Helen Glover will go for gold in the women's four - assuming she makes the final.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1563, \"end\": 1575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\", \"score\": 0.9968858553495725, \"rank\": 0.0031234382808593376, \"text\": \"Helen Glover\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the highs of London 2012 and Rio 2016 the medal haul in Tokyo was more than disappointing.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1665, \"end\": 1676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.223757031909814e-14, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1708, \"end\": 1713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8975011877285911, \"rank\": 0.11420465361521244, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB are back and looking to restore some pride.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999962178663, \"rank\": 3.340421591465083e-09, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Equestrian has been in the news for the wrong reasons recently but the British team jumping team will undoubtedly be in the mix for gold.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1868, \"end\": 1875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9942513182200073, \"rank\": 0.005777907252568181, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a sport of great control and skill and it is something Team GB have been strong at in the past.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1997, \"end\": 2004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999962178663, \"rank\": 3.340421591465083e-09, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Max Whitlock is back and going for gold in his final games.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit, alongside his fellow countrymen and women, have a number of medal chances across gymnastics but a Whitlock win would be brilliant for fans of the sport.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2208, \"end\": 2216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.944141045736323e-12, \"text\": \"Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": 